<!-- WHAT THIS IS -->
<!-- ========================= -->
<section class="alchemy-section">
  <div class="alchemy-wrap narrow">
    <h2>What this is</h2>
    <p>
      Most change efforts fail because they stay on the surface: tools, strategy, behavior tips.
      Alchemy works deeper — at the level of meaning-making and survival patterns.
      That’s where the loop actually lives.
    </p>

    <ul class="alchemy-bullets">
      <li><strong>Facilitated:</strong> a trained guide keeps the session out of blame and inside observation.</li>
      <li><strong>Experiential:</strong> structured prompts surface real patterns quickly without forced disclosure.</li>
      <li><strong>Practical:</strong> each session ends with one small, testable shift the team can apply immediately.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

