<!-- ========================= -->
<!-- HOW A SESSION WORKS -->
<!-- ========================= -->
<section class="alchemy-section">
  <div class="alchemy-wrap narrow">
    <h2>How a session works</h2>

    <div class="alchemy-steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Orientation</h3>
          <p>Set a simple container: observe patterns, avoid blame, stay present, stay honest.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Pattern selection</h3>
          <p>Participants choose prompts that match what’s happening now (no randomness required).</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Facilitated reflection</h3>
          <p>Name the loop: what triggers it, what it protects, and what it costs the team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3>One practical shift</h3>
          <p>Choose one small action that changes the loop: a phrase, a boundary, a meeting rule, a practice.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sessions-box">
      <div class="meta-title">Mid-session holding question</div>
      <div class="meta-sub">“What is this pattern trying to protect — and what is it costing us?”</div>
      <div class="small" style="margin-top: 10px;">
        If the group drifts into debate, advice, or blame, return to the question.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

